### Get all movies
GET http://localhost:8080/movies

### Get movie by id
GET http://localhost:8080/movies/2

### Create new movie
POST http://localhost:8080/movies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "new-movie"
}

### Delete movie by id
DELETE http://localhost:8080/movies/1

### Update movie
PATCH http://localhost:8080/movies/10
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "new-movie10"
}
